{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_014EwXsu6WZJeMEZwT2oXLn1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cluster health returns 503 because the master isn't discovered yet. The cluster can't form because:\n\n1. es-0 is failing the readiness probe (probe timeout is too short), so es-1 and es-2 don't start\n2. es-0 can't resolve `es-headless` to find other nodes\n\nBut even before that, `cluster.initial_master_nodes` requires at least a quorum. Let me think about this differently.\n\nThe real issue is:\n1. The readiness probe checks `_cluster/health` which requires a formed cluster\n2. But the cluster can't form until all 3 nodes are running (because `initial_master_nodes` is set to all 3)\n3. And es-1 and es-2 won't start until es-0 passes its readiness check\n\nThis is a deadlock. The best fix is to switch to parallel pod management so all three nodes start simultaneously, allowing the cluster to form. I also need to increase the readiness probe timeout, use the full domain name for discovery, and add the parallel pod management policy.\n\nNow I'm thinking through how to apply these changes. I can't just patch the StatefulSet since pod management policy can't be updated that way—I'll need to delete and recreate it while preserving the existing PVCs using `--cascade=orphan`.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":824,"cache_read_input_tokens":35960,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":824},"output_tokens":29,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1811e6eb-b38e-40db-9434-e262aa5d8108","uuid":"5a92f78b-6a45-4788-bf79-e801b2f1f42c","request_id":"req_011CcQRBKjVndbyKVzfsBgqh"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_014EwXsu6WZJeMEZwT2oXLn1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"There's a deadlock: the readiness probe checks cluster health, but the cluster can't form until all 3 pods are up, and the StatefulSet won't start es-1/es-2 until es-0 is Ready. Fix with `podManagementPolicy: Parallel` and a longer probe timeout, plus FQDN for discovery."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":824,"cache_read_input_tokens":35960,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":824},"output_tokens":29,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1811e6eb-b38e-40db-9434-e262aa5d8108","uuid":"aed3b661-4394-492e-a4bd-a75b68c4746e","request_id":"req_011CcQRBKjVndbyKVzfsBgqh"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_014EwXsu6WZJeMEZwT2oXLn1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01J447dTFyRUncAdLjs8YBB8","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"# Delete just the StatefulSet (keep PVCs and pods running for now)\nkubectl delete statefulset es -n elasticsearch --cascade=orphan\n# Update the ConfigMap with FQDN\nkubectl patch configmap es-config -n elasticsearch --type merge -p '{\"data\":{\"elasticsearch.yml\":\"cluster.name: \\\"es-cluster\\\"\\nnetwork.host: \\\"0.0.0.0\\\"\\ndiscovery.seed_hosts: \\\"es-headless.elasticsearch.svc.cluster.local\\\"\\ncluster.initial_master_nodes: \\\"es-0,es-1,es-2\\\"\\nxpack.security.enabled: \\\"true\\\"\\nxpack.security.http.ssl.enabled: \\\"true\\\"\\nxpack.security.http.ssl.key: /usr/share/elasticsearch/config/certs/tls.key\\nxpack.security.http.ssl.certificate: /usr/share/elasticsearch/config/certs/tls.crt\\nxpack.security.http.ssl.certificate_authorities: /usr/share/elasticsearch/config/certs/ca.crt\\nxpack.security.transport.ssl.enabled: \\\"true\\\"\\nxpack.security.transport.ssl.key: /usr/share/elasticsearch/config/certs/tls.key\\nxpack.security.transport.ssl.certificate: /usr/share/elasticsearch/config/certs/tls.crt\\nxpack.security.transport.ssl.certificate_authorities: /usr/share/elasticsearch/config/certs/ca.crt\\nxpack.security.transport.ssl.verification_mode: certificate\\n\"}}'","description":"Delete StatefulSet (keep pods/PVCs) and update ConfigMap with FQDN"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":824,"cache_read_input_tokens":35960,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":824},"output_tokens":29,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1811e6eb-b38e-40db-9434-e262aa5d8108","uuid":"15c